title: Nils Althin
text: Nils Althin (12 May 1905 – 19 May 1978) was a Swedish <a href="boxing">boxer</a>. He competed in the <a href="Boxing%20at%20the%201932%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Men%27s%20welterweight">men's welterweight</a> event at the <a href="1932%20Summer%20Olympics">1932 Summer Olympics</a>.
